KATSINA – The management of Uma­ru Musa Yar’adua Univer­sity, (UMYU), Katsina, has expressed its readiness to sponsor a professor in each faculty on one week research training in any foreign uni­versity from next academic session. In a statement signed by AbdulHamid Danjuma, the institution’s head of Infor­mation and Protocols and made available to newsmen in Katsina on Tuesday, the VC Prof. Sanusi Mamman, said this at the end of a train­ing workshop on capacity building for staff of the in­stitution. Mamman said the foreign training for the professors was meant to open more opportunities for the aca­demic staff to acquire addi­tional and relevant skills to fast track the growth of the university. EXPOSED - HOW LAGOS DOCTOR DISCOVERED MAJOR REASONS WHY MOST WIVES NOW HEAVILY CHEATS ON THEIR HUSBANDS AND THE PERMANENT SECRET TO SEXUALLY SATISFYING THEIR WIVES. DON'T BE A VICTIM! “The institution needs the versatile experience of each and every academic staff to help in realizing its goals in learning, teaching and train­ing of the upcoming leaders of tomorrow,” he said. SHOCKING! DOCTORS ARE MESMERIZED BY THIS NATURAL PREMATURE EJACULATION AND SMALL SIZE SOLUTION GUARANTEED TO BULLDOZE YOUR WOMAN INTO SEXUAL SUBMISSION